name: Kids Art Print - "Foxy Mama"
description:
This print is the first in my Oregon inspired series. Titled "Foxy Mama", it is a print of my original digital illustration. Perfect for a woodland themed nursery or child's room.

This is a single 8x10 inch print on an 8.5x11 inch paper size
Printed on bright white, archival, 310 gsm high quality rag paper.
Acid free, smooth, matte finish with vibrant color
Signed and dated on the back

Shipped in a clear, sealed cello sleeve with a rigid backing in a stay-flat mailer

Watermark will not appear on the actual print

FRAME AND MAT NOT INCLUDED

***Colors may vary due to monitor differences
